data.description: Wonderful recently updated 4BR 3 full bath home with bonus room.  New roof, new HVAC,  new hardwoods in living areas, new paint downstairs.  Dishwasher and stove less than 1 year old.  Granite in kitchen with stainless appliances, all kitchen appliances and washer and dryer included!  Formal dining room,  gas fireplace in living room.  3 bedrooms and 2 baths on 1st floor with 4th bedroom, full bath and bonus upstairs, giving you so many options such as second master , inlaw or guest suite.  Huge fenced  backyard w/ screened porch and patio.  Excellent location, just 20-25 min commute to Fort Liberty,  Pope Field and Fayetteville, within an hour to Raleigh / Cary.  This is a great one to call HOME.
